---

<BaseLayout
  title="Lace Boss Guide - Hollow Knight: Silksong"
  description="Complete strategy guide for defeating Lace in Hollow Knight: Silksong. Learn her attack patterns, best tactics, and recommended tools."
  keywords="lace boss guide, silksong lace strategy, lace boss fight, hollow knight silksong bosses"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
