                <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-300 text-sm">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Moderate aggression</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Standard attack patterns</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Predictable movement</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Short recovery windows</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">Strategy:</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-300 text-sm">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Learn her attack patterns</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Focus on safe damage</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Conserve healing items</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Position for next phase</li>
